ded bosses<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Now with music!<br><br>Requests from previous games realized:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Remap controls option, warping, retry faster after falling, more dynamic layouts",
